text.section:
A partnership may file a statement of partnership authority, which:
Shall include:
The name of the partnership, which shall comply with KRS 14A.3-010;
The street address of its chief executive office and of one (1) office in this Commonwealth, if any;
The names and mailing addresses of all of the partners or of an agent appointed and maintained by the partnership for the purpose of subsection (2) of this section;
The names of the partners authorized to execute an instrument transferring real property held in the name of the partnership;
The date any statement of qualification or statement of foreign qualification was previously filed by the partnership with the Secretary of State; and
May state the authority, or limitations on the authority, of some or all of the partners to enter into other transactions on behalf of the partnership and any other matter.
